    Decision logs / design rationale (a lot of what's in your MAP-System.zip reference series) are exactly the kind of thing that benefits from backlinks — "why did we choose atomic task ID allocation" links naturally to the repo-drift and locking docs.

Where it'd be friction for you specifically:

